      "description": "This build focuses on maximum control and constant mid-game pressure. Magic Shoes and Enchanted Talisman provide cooldown reduction and unlimited mana sustain, allowing continuous skill spam to dominate the wave and control rotations. Glowing Wand is the core of the build, enhancing damage over time and punishing any form of sustain. Ice Queen Wand adds heavy control with consistent slows, making it easier to kite fighters and assassins. Wishing Lantern increases damage against high-HP enemies, making Valir extremely effective against frontliners. Divine Glaive completes the build by providing magic penetration in the late game, ensuring your damage remains impactful even against high magic resistance.\n\nThe goal is not instant burst, but sustained damage, zoning control, and anti-engage power. Ideal against tanky or dive-heavy compositions, this build excels in extended teamfights and allows you to dictate the pace of the match.",
